<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:grantha maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> pañcōpētatriśatasahitēva</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">tsarāṇām sahasrē śākē yātē ta</hi>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">danu rudhirōtgāri samvatsarasya <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> jā</hi>
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">tē māsē tapanaśaśinōḥ kārttikē śu</hi>
<lb n="5"/><hi rend="grantha">klapakṣē rēvattyēkādaśatithiyutē</hi>
<lb n="6"/><hi rend="grantha">daityapūjyasya vārē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></hi>
<lb n="7"/><hi rend="grantha">Asti śrīmān kumārō hariharanṛpatēśśrī vi</hi>
<lb n="8" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">rūpākṣanāmā (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) tanmantrī muddapāryyō vimala</hi>
</p>

<p>1. The length sign is engraved below the line.</p> 

<p>
<lb n="9" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">guṇagaṇō gōtrajaḥ kāśyapasya <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></hi>
<lb n="10"/><hi rend="grantha">prādācśrīraṅgadhāmnē muradanujabhidē sannidhēḥ</hi>
<lb n="11"/><hi rend="grantha">pūrvabhāgē nityāyai dīpikāyai niravadhika</hi>
<lb n="12"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>ba</unclear>lāp<unclear>ē</unclear>kṣayā vimśatim gāḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></hi>
</p>

